  "text": "In this paper, we will concentrate on the first question only to explore the weight design, and through which a heuristic extended EM (X-EM) algorithm is presented accordingly. Keeping the number of model components unchanged, this new algorithm updates the parameters analogous to the EM [CITATION_1] , and is able to perform the model selection by fading the redundant components out from a density mixture during the parameter learning process. Experimental results have shown the efficacy of our algorithm.",
